comments: The app did not record trips many times, I remembered 15 trips done; however, the app just recorded 5. The button for stopping the app is confusing

The app often didn't work correctly and especially worldn't count correctly. I found it hard to choose tags for each journey. It would be good if you could edit your former journeys (I sometimes started new ones by mistake and couldn't add tags)
Eventhough I did some trips, it only showed 3 trips at the end of the experiment. If the app would have worked correctly, it would have been more enjoyable to use the app.
I would forget to use the app sometimes, I would close the app sometimes after the trip finished

The counter for the trips ("Ausfluge") did not change (remained zero), even after completing various trops. Therefore, I was not sure, if the app was working properly / In general, a very cool idea that will make cycling more enjoyable
A reminder to use the app would be good, It istarts alternativelly when you ride your bike
I didn't explore the app further | the app should have a reminder for its use. I forgot frequently to use it
I never used the leaderboard: Maybe if it includes people from my curcle of friends, I'd be intereste to compete against them
I use the bike everyday, Difficult to always use the app | a fitness app gives you more accurate info
I found it really hard to remember to taken on the app when going cycling. Perhaps you could implement the possibility to turn on a reminder
